Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Keshav%20Prasad%20Maurya%20met%20BJP%20chief%20J%20P%20Nadda%20last%20evening.%20He%20left%20the%20BJP%20headquarters%20without%20speaking%20to%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20suggest%20Mr%20Nadda%20may%20also%20meet%20UP%20BJP%20chief%20Bhupendra%20Singh%20Chaudhary%2C%20but%20there%20has%20been%20no%20official%20word%20on%20the%20meeting's%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Adityanath%20had%20at%20a%20conclave%20blamed%20%26quot%3Bover-confidence%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20poor%20electoral%20performance%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20suggested%20the%20BJP%20could%20not%20effectively%20counter%20the%20INDIA%20bloc's%20campaign.%20Mr%20Nadda%20was%20present%20at%20the%20conclave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20BJP%20saw%20an%20overall%20drop%20in%20seats%20as%20it%20failed%20to%20secure%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20discuss%20its%20performance%2C%20the%20party%20has%20called%20all%20its%20chief%20ministers%20and%20their%20deputies%20to%20Delhi%20at%20the%20end%20of%20this%20month.%20Modi%203.0's%20first%20budget%20and%20the%20action%20plan%20for%20the%20first%20100%20days%20will%20also%20be%20discussed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%2C%20and%20BJP%20chief%20JP%20Nadda%20are%20among%20the%20senior%20BJP%20leaders%20set%20to%20attend%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721194380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F1aeots2o_cm-yogi-adityanath_625x300_14_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-huddle-in-up-today-to-review-bypoll-preps-after-lok-sabha-setback-6123231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Top%20BJP%20leaders%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20will%20meet%20this%20morning%20to%20review%20preparations%20for%20the%20upcoming%20by-elections%20t