0Educational%20criteria%20for%20the%20job%20are%20basic%2C%20but%20the%20candidate%20must%20be%20physically%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20aspirants%20is%20Prathameshwar%20from%20Buldhana%20district%2C%20who%20has%20travelled%20over%20400%20km%20for%20the%20interview.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20come%20to%20apply%20for%20the%20post%20of%20handyman.%20They%20are%20offering%20a%20salary%20of%20Rs%2022%2C500%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Prathameshwar%20is%20a%20second%20year%20BBA%20student.%20Asked%20if%20he%20would%20quit%20his%20studies%20if%20he%20gets%20the%20job%2C%20he%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20do%20we%20do%3F%20There%20is%20so%20much%20unemployment.%20I%20urge%20the%20government%20to%20create%20more%20job%20opportunities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20aspirant%20who%20has%20BA%20degree%20said%20he%20does%20not%20know%20much%20about%20the%20work%20of%20a%20handyman%2C%20but%20says%20he%20%26quot%3Bneeds%20the%20job%26quot%3B.%20Another%20candidate%20has%20travelled%20from%20Rajasthan's%20Alwar%20to%20Mumbai.%20He%20has%20an%20MCom%20degree%2C%20but%20has%20applied%20for%20a%20job%20that%20has%20a%20basic%20education%20requirement.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20preparing%20for%20government%20job%20exams%20as%20well%2C%20someone%20told%20me%20that%20the%20salary%20here%20is%20good.%20So%20I%20have%20come.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mumbai%20incident%20comes%20days%20after%20a%20viral%20video%20showed%20hundreds%20of%20jobseekers%20pushing%20and%20shoving%20each%20other%20at%20a%20walk-in%20interview%20at%20Ankleshwar%20in%20Gujarat's%20Bharuch%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%201%2C800%20aspirants%20had%20turned%20up%20for%20a%20recruitment%20drive%20for%20just%2010%20posts%20in%20a%20private%20firm.%20Such%20was%20the%20rush%20that%20a%20railing%20on%20the%20ramp%20leading%20to%20the%20office's%20entry%20collapsed%20under%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20jobseekers.%20Fortunately%2C%20the%20ramp%20was%20not%20very%20high%2C%20and%20none%20of%20the%20aspirants%20who%20lost%20their%20balance%20after%20the%20railing%20collapsed%20suffered%20serious%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELatching%20on%20to%20the%20video%2C%20the%20Congress%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bexposed%20the%20BJP's%20Gujarat%20model%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20the%20ruling%20party%20was%20imposing%20this%20model%20of%20unemployment%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20BJP%20MP%20Mansukh%20Vasava%20blamed%20the%20private%20firm%20for%20the%20incident.%20%26quot%3BThey%20were%20filling%20up%20only%2010%20vacancies%20and%20should%20have%20specified%20the%20criteria%20properly%20instead%20of%20holding%20an%20open%20interview.%20At%20some%20level%2C%20the%20incident%20occurred%20because%20of%20the%20company.%20We%20are%20worried%20about%20it%20and%20steps%20are%20being%20taken%20to%20ensure%20such%20incidents%20don't%20happen%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mumbai%20airport%20video%2C%20too%2C%20has%20prompted%20Congress%20MP%20Varsha%20Gaikwad%20to%20raise%20the%20unemployment%20issue%20and%20target%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mumbai%20North%20Central%20MP%20said%20that%20the%20unemployment%20situation%20has%20become%20so%20bad%20in%20the%20past%2010%20years%20that%20youngsters%20are%20ready%20to%20fight%20wars%20for%20Russia%20and%20Israel.%20%26quot%3BWhenever%20they%20hear%20of%20jobs%2C%20they%20gather%20in%20thousands%20and%20there%20is%20a%20fear%20of%20stampede%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20a%20Hindi%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20India%20is%20yet%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20viral%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721194380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F9vnumc7o_mumbai-airport_625x300_17_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fair-india-mumbai-airport-600-jobs-25-000-seekers-air-india-drive-sets-off-stampede-fear-in-mumbai-6122988%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Air%20India%20recruitment%20drive%20for%20airpor