ublican%20Event%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20homeless%20black%20man%2C%20armed%20with%20two%20knives%20near%20a%20Republican%20Party%20National%20Convention%20site%20in%20Wisconsin%2C%20was%20shot%20dead%20by%20police%20officers%20from%20Ohio%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20the%20man%2C%20identified%20by%20relatives%20as%2043-year-old%20Samuel%20Sharpe%2C%20was%20armed%20with%20a%20knife%20in%20each%20hand.%20The%20situation%20escalated%20when%20Sharpe%20charged%20at%20an%20unarmed%20individual%2C%20prompting%20the%20officers%20to%20open%20fire.%20Two%20knives%20were%20recovered%20from%20the%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomeone's%20life%20was%20in%20danger%2C%26quot%3B%20Milwaukee%20police%20chief%20Jeffrey%20Norman%20said%20during%20a%20press%20conference.%20%26quot%3BThese%20officers%2C%20who%20were%20not%20from%20this%20area%2C%20took%20it%20upon%20themselves%20to%20act%20and%20save%20someone's%20life%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20occurred%20amidst%20heightened%20security%20in%20Milwaukee%2C%20with%20thousands%20of%20officers%20from%20various%20jurisdictions%20present%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20Republican%20National%20Convention%2C%20which%20started%20on%20Monday%20and%20is%20set%20to%20conclude%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shooting%2C%20however%2C%20has%20sparked%20outrage%20among%20Milwaukee%20residents%2C%20who%20questioned%20the%20necessity%20of%20out-of-state%20officers%20patrolling%20their%20neighbourhood%2C%20which%20is%20located%20over%20a%20kilometre%20away%20from%20the%20convention%20site.%20Many%20locals%20gathered%20at%20the%20scene%2C%20voicing%20their%20anger%20and%20planning%20a%20nighttime%20vigil%20to%20honour%20Sharpe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20came%20into%20our%20community%20and%20shot%20down%20our%20family%20right%20here%20at%20a%20public%20park%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Linda%20Sharpe%2C%20Samuel's%20cousin.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20