r%20skill%20isn't%20the%20only%20thing%20that%20is%20required%20to%20consistently%20remain%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20team%2C%20being%20liked%20is%20also%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20liked%20matters%20a%20lot%20in%20team%20selection.%20Just%20playing%20good%20cricket%20isn't%20enough.%20The%20captain%20always%20decides%20the%20Playing%20XI.%20I%20had%20an%20excellent%20rapport%20with%20MS%20Dhoni.%20I%20asked%20him%20twice%20why%20I%20wasn't%20getting%20picked%2C%20he%20told%20me%20that%20I%20don't%20fit%20the%20combination%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20told%20that%20I%20was%20being%20given%20a%20rest.%20I%20never%20asked%20for%20it.%20I%20hadn't%20even%20played%2010%20Test%20matches%20by%20then%2C%20why%20would%20I%20ask%20for%20a%20rest%20or%20break%3F%20If%20I%20have%20to%20tell%20you%20honestly%2C%20I%20wasn't%20in%20a%20position%20%5Bto%20question%20Dhoni%5D.%20Yes%2C%20I%20asked%20the%20coach%2C%20and%20he%20told%20me%20to%20go%20ask%20Dhoni%2C%20but%20like%20I%20said%2C%20I%20wasn't%20in%20that%20position%20to%20go%20and%20ask%20Dhoni.%20I%20asked%20the%20coach%20again%20and%20he%20just%20said%20we%20are%20giving%20you%20rest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMishra%20then%20revealed%20the%20'worst%20feeling'%20he%20ever%20got%20in%20his%20career%2C%20saying%20he%20was%20forced%20to%20take%20rest%20after%20picking%20up%20a%20knee%20injury.%20While%20the%20rule%20was%20that%20injured%20players%2C%20upon%20making%20full%20recovery%2C%20were%20automatically%20selected%20in%20the%20team%2C%20the%20same%20didn't%20happen%20with%20Mishra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20worst%20I've%20felt%20in%20my%20career%20was%20when%20I%20picked%20up%20a%20knee%20injury%20five%20years%20ago.%20It%20happened%20in%20between%20the%20match.%20The%20series%20before%20I%20was%20the%20Man%20of%20the%20Series%20and%20the%20Man%20of%20the%20match%20against%20New%20Zealand.%20And%20this%20used%20to%20be%20t