0said%20'I'll%20let%20you%20know'%20but%20never%20did%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721182260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fp58m7348_virat-kohli_625x300_27_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fasked-virat-kohli-to-give-clear-picture-he-never-did-veteran-spinners-big-accusation-6115064%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Veteran%20India%20spinner%20Amit%20Mishra%20made%20a%20big%20accusation%20on%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20saying%20the%20former%20skipper%20never%20gave%20him%20a%20clear%20answer%20about%20his%20non-selection%20in%20team%2C%20despite%20being%20asked.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fasked-virat-kohli-to-give-clear-picture-he-never-did-veteran-spinners-big-accusation-6115064%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fasked-virat-kohli-to-give-clear-picture-he-never-did-veteran-spinners-big-accusation-6115064%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fasked-virat-kohli-to-give-clear-picture-he-never-did-veteran-spinners-big-accusation-6115064%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20says%20Taiwan%20should%20pay%20for%20defence%2C%20sending%20TSMC%20stock%20down%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721182190000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111796933%2Cimgsize-27638.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftrump-says-taiwan-should-pay-for-defence-sending-tsmc-stock-down%2Farticleshow%2F111796933.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F111796933.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https