0the%202025%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20with%20the%202027%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20being%20the%20ultimate%20prize.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20of%20the%20heroes%20of%20India's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20victory%20last%20month%20will%20take%20a%20break%20during%20the%20three-match%20ODI%20series%2C%20which%20is%20scheduled%20in%20August%2C%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%20reasons%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20confirmed%20to%20PTI%20that%C2%A0Pandya%C2%A0has%20asked%20for%20leave%20and%20has%20already%20communicated%20this%20to%20regular%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20who%20is%20also%20taking%20a%20break%20from%20this%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20break%20from%20ODIs%20is%20for%20very%20personal%20reasons.%C2%A0Hardik%C2%A0doesn't%20have%20any%20fitness%20issue%20as%20is%20being%20floated%20in%20the%20media%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20ODIs%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22KL%20Rahul%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1688-lokesh-rahul-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKL%20Rahul%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20led%20in%20the%20last%20ODI%20series%20in%20South%20Africa%2C%20and%20Gill%20are%20in%20contention%20for%20the%20leadership%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20another%20report%20in%20the%20PTI%20has%20made%20a%20big%20claim.%20The%20report%20said%20Suryakumar%C2%A0Yadav%C2%A0has%20emerged%20as%20the%20dark%20horse%20to%20become%20India's%20T20%20captain%20till%20the%202026%20World%20Cup%20and%20might%20just%20pip%20top%20contender%20Hardik%20Pandya%2C%20whose%20elevation%20from%20the%20vice-captain's%20position%20was%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20natural%20progression%20up%20until%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandya%20made%20himself%20available%20for%20the%20shortest%20format%20games%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%20this%20month%20but%20it%20has%20emerged%20that%C2%A0Suryakumar%2C%20who%20captained%20India%20in%20eight%20T20Is%20against%20Australia%20and%20South%20Africa%20last%20year%2C%20is%20the%20preferred%20choice%20of%20new%20head%20coach%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20and%20chairman%20of%20selectors%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ajit%20Agarkar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F100-ajit-agarkar-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAjit%20Agarkar%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPTI%20said%20both%20Gambhir%20and%20Agarkar%20spoke%20to%20Pandya%20about%20this%20change%20of%20plan%20earlier%20this%20evening%20and%20explained%20to%20him%20that%20a%20long-term%20option%20was%20being%20finalised%20to%20ensure%20stability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20T20%20leadership%20role%20fell%20vacant%20after%20Rohit%20Sharma%20bid%20adieu%20to%20his%20international%20career%20in%20the%20shortest%20format%20following%20India's%20World%20Cup%20triumph%20last%20month%20in%20the%20West%20Indies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721182020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F389gmsgg_shubman-gill-kl-rahul-afp_625x300_24_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fignored-for-t20-world-cup-india-star-among-top-two-contenders-for-odi-captaincy-vs-sri-lanka-report-6121201%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20will%20play%20three%20T20Is%20and%20three%20ODIs%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fignored-for-t20-world-cup-india-star-among-top-two-contenders-for-odi-captaincy-vs-sri-lanka-report-6121201%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fignored-for-t20-world-cup-india-star-among-top-two-contenders-for-odi-captaincy-vs-sri-lanka-report-6121201%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fignored-for-t20-world-cup-india-star-among-top-two-contenders-for-odi-captaincy-vs-sri-lanka-report-6121201%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Got%20Intel%20About%20Iranian%20Plot%20To%20Kill%20Trump%20Weeks%20Before%20Rally%20Shooting%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20had%20received%20intelligence%20from%20a%20human%20source%20about%20an%20Iranian%20plot%20to%20kill%20Donald%20Trump%20weeks%20before%20the%20assassination%20attempt%20against%20the%20former%20US%20president%20on%20Saturday%2C%20according%20to%20national%20security%20officials.%20This%20led%20to%20increased%20security%20measures%20for%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20there%20is%20no%20known%20connection%20between%20this%20Iranian%20plot%20and%20the%2020-year-old%20who%20attempted%20to%20assassinate%20Trump%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Secret%20Service%20and%20the%20Trump%20campaign%20were%20notified%20of%20the%20Iranian%20threat%2C%20and%20security%20was%20boosted%20as%20a%20result%2C%20as%20confirmed%20by%20a%20US%20national%20security%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20and%20his%20former%20secretary%20of%20state%2C%20Mike%20Pompeo%2C%20have%20faced%20threats%20from%20Tehran%20since%20the%202020%20drone%20strike%20that%20killed%20Qassim%20Soleimani%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20Iran's%20Quds%20force%2C%20in%20Iraq.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnthony%20Guglielmi%2C%20a%20spokesman%20for%20the%20US%20Secret%20Service%2C%20said%20that%20it%20and%20other%20agencies%20were%20%26quot%3Bconstantly%20receiving%20new%20potential%20threat%20information%20and%20taking%20action%20to%20adjust%20resources%20as%20needed.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20cannot%20comment%20on%20any%20specific%20threat%20stream%2C%20other%20than%20to%20say%20that%20the%20Secret%20Service%20takes%20threats%20seriously%20and%20responds%20accordingly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdrienne%20Watson%2C%20a%20spokeswoman%20for%20the%20White%20House%20National%20Security%20Council%2C%20said%20that%20US%20security%20officials%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Btracking%20Iranian%20threats%20against%20former%20Trump%20administration%20officials%20for%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Iranian%20mission%20at%20the%20United%20Nations%20dismissed%20the%20report%20as%20%26quot%3Bunsubstantiated%20and%20malicious%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bis%20a%20criminal%20who%20must%20be%20prosecuted%20and%20punished%20in%20a%20court%20of%20law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20made%20his%20first%20public%20appearance%20at%20the%20Republican%20National%20Convention%20on%20Monday%20(local%20time)%20since%20surviving%20the%20assassination%20attempt%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWearing%20a%20white%20bandage%20on%20his%20right%20ear%2C%20Trump%20waved%20at%20supporters%20and%20received%20a%20standing%20ovation%20from%20the%20audience.%20He%20made%20no%20remarks%20during%20the%20convention%20and%20stood%20alongside%20his%20newly%20announced%20running%20mate%2C%20Senator%20JD%20Vance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20was%20on%20stage%20at%20a%20campaign%20rally%20on%20Saturday%20when%20gunshots%20rang%20out%20and%20Secret%20Service%20agents%20stormed%20the%20stage.%20Hours%20after%20the%20shooting%2C%20Trump%20said%20that%20the%20bullet%20pierced%20the%20upper%20part%20of%20his%20right%20ear.%20One%20of%20the%20rally%20attendees%20was%20killed%2C%20while%20two%20more%20were%20critically%20injured%20in%20the%20shooting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(FBI)%20identified%20the%20shooter%20as%20Thomas%20Matthew%20Crooks%2C%2020%2C%20from%20Bethel%20Park%2C%20Pennsylvania.%20The%20case%20remains%20under%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721181960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fjv1gl7do_trump-shooting_625x300_14_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-got-intel-about-iranian-plot-to-kill-trump-weeks-before-rally-shooting-6122411%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20United%20States%20had%20received%20intelligence%20from%20a%20human%20source%20about%20an%20Iranian%20plot%20to%20kill%20Donald%20Trump%20weeks%20before%20the%20assassination%20attempt%20against%20the%20former%20US%20president%20on%20Saturday%2C%20according%20to%20national%20security%20officials.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-got-intel-about-iranian-plot-to-kill-trump-weeks-before-rally-shooting-6122411%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-got-intel-about-iranian-plot-to-kill-trump-weeks-before-rally-shooting-6122411%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-got-intel-about-iranian-plot-to-kill-trump-weeks-before-rally-shooting-6122411%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Six%20students%20killed%20in%20Bangladesh%20protest%20against%20quota%20system%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721181461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111796512%2Cimgsize-1836264.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fsix-students-killed-in-bangladesh-protest-against-quota-system%2Farticleshow%2F111796415.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F111796415.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESix%20students%20were%20killed%20in%20violent%20protests%20against%20the%20quota%20system%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20leading%20to%20nationwide%20school%20closures.%20Demonstrators%20continue%20to%20mobilize%20despite%20calls%20to%20return%20to%20class.%20International%20bodies%20have%20urged%20the%20government%20to%20protect%20peaceful%20protesters%20and%20guarantee%20their%20safety.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fsix-students-killed-in-bangladesh-protest-against-quota-system%2Farticleshow%2F111796415.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fsix-students-killed-in-bangladesh-protest-against-quota-system%2Famp_articleshow%2F111796415.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fsix-students-killed-in-bangladesh-protest-against-quota-system%2Famp_articleshow%2F111796415.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20IAS%20Officer%20Puja%20Khedkar's%20Training%20Has%20Been%20Put%20On%20Hold%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20training%20of%20probationary%20IAS%20officer%20Puja%20Khedkar%20has%20been%20put%20on%20hold%20amid%20allegations%20of%20misuse%20of%20power%20and%20privileges.%20Ms%20Khedkar%20has%20been%20recalled%20to%20the%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Shastri%20National%20Academy%20of%20Administration%20(LBSNAA)%20in%20Mussoorie%20for%20%26quot%3Bfurther%20necessary%20action%26quot%3B.%20Ms%20Khedkar%20was%20earlier%20transferred%20to%20Washim%20from%20Pune%20following%20accusations%20of%20manipulating%20disability%20and%20OBC%20certificates%20to%20gain%20entry%20into%20the%20civil%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20General%20Administration%20Department%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20issued%20a%20directive%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20hereby%20relieved%20from%20the%20District%20Training%20Programme%20of%20the%20State%20Government%20of%20Maharashtra.%26quot%3B%20The%20directive%20instructs%20Ms%20Khedkar%20to%20%26quot%3Bjoin%20the%20academy%20at%20the%20earliest%26quot%3B%20but%20not%20later%20than%20July%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Khedkar%2C%20a%202023-batch%20officer%20from%20Ahmednagar%2C%20claims%20to%20be%20the%20victim%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bmedia%20trial%26quot%3B%20alleging%20that%20a%20misinformation%20campaign%20has%20been%20waged%20against%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authenticity%20of%20various%20certificates%20submitted%20by%20Ms%20Khedkar%20to%20the%20Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(UPSC)%20is%20currently%20under%20investigation.%20These%20include%20certificates%20indicating%20visual%20impairment%2C%20which%20Ms%20Khedkar%20submitted%20under%20the%20Persons%20with%20Benchmark%20Disabilities%20(PwBD)%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20referred%20by%20the%20UPSC%20for%20a%20medical%20examination%20at%20Delhi's%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20(AIIMS)%2C%20Ms%20Khedkar%20reportedly%20missed%20six%20appointments%20between%20April%20and%20August%202022.%20In%20August%202022%2C%20she%20applied%20for%20another%20disability%20certificate%20from%20the%20Aundh%20government%20hospital%20in%20Pune%2C%20but%20her%20application%20was%20rejected%20following%20medical%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Khedkar's%20troubles%20began%20when%20she%20was%20accused%20of%20demanding%20unauthorised%20perks%20and%20facilities%20while%20serving%20as%20an%20assistant%20collector%20in%20Pune.%20Allegations%20include%20using%20a%20red%20beacon%20and%20a%20%26quot%3BGovernment%20of%20Maharashtra%26quot%3B%20sticker%20on%20her%20private%20Audi%20car%2C%20occupying%20the%20office%20of%20Pune%20Additional%20Collector%20Ajay%20More%20during%20his%20absence%2C%20and%20demanding%20office%20furniture%2C%20letterheads%2C%20a%20VIP%20number%20plate%2C%20a%20separate%20house%2C%20and%20a%20car.%20These%20perks%20are%20typically%20unavailable%20to%20probationary%20officers%20who%20are%20still%20in%20their%2024-month%20probationary%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20these%20allegations%2C%20Ms%20Khedkar%20was%20transferred%20from%20Pune%20to%20Washim%20as%20a%20supernumerary%20assistant%20collector.%20This%20move%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20temporary%20measure%20pending%20further%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20RTI%20activist%20from%20Pune%2C%20Vijay%20Kumbhar%2C%20alleged%20that%20Ms%20Khedkar's%20father%20possessed%20assets%20worth%20Rs%2040%20crore%2C%20which%20would%20place%20the%20family%20well%20above%20the%20Rs%208%20lakh%20annual%20income%20threshold%20for%20any%20reservation%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Khedkar%20has%20stated%20her%20willingness%20to%20testify%20before%20the%20expert%20committee%2C%20expressing%20confidence%20that%20the%20truth%20will%20emerge.%20%26quot%3BWhatever%20my%20submission%20is%2C%20I%20will%20give%20it%20in%20front%20of%20the%20committee%20and%20the%20truth%20will%20come%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pune%20Police%20are%20also%20investigating%20Ms%20Khedkar's%20parents%20in%20a%20criminal%20case%20involving%20her%20mother%2C%20Manorama%20Khedkar%2C%20a%20village%20sarpanch%2C%20who%20was%20allegedly%20seen%20threatening%20individuals%20with%20a%20gun%20over%20a%20land%20dispute%20in%20a%20video.%20An%20FIR%20has%20been%20filed%20against%20the%20couple%20and%20five%20others%20in%20connection%20with%20this%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Khedkar%20has%20lodged%20a%20harassment%20complaint%20against%20Pune%20district%20collector%20Suhas%20Diwase.%20According%20to%20an%20official%2C%20women%20police%20personnel%20visited%20Ms%20Khedkar%20at%20her%20residence%20in%20Washim%2C%20where%20she%20filed%20the%20complaint.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721181360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F8lvtkuho_puja-khedkar_625x300_12_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-trainee-ias-officer-puja-khedkars-training-has-been-put-on-hold-