example%2C%20in%20a%20series%20of%20rulings%20this%20term%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupreme-court-rulings-executive-power-grab-strengthen-judiciary-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeroded%20the%20power%20of%20the%20executive%20branch%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20rolling%20back%20the%20power%20of%20administrative%20positions%20in%20the%20executive%20branch%20while%20strengthening%20the%20presidency%20itself.%20The%20rulings%20%E2%80%94%20made%20by%20a%20polarized%2C%20conservative-majority%20court%20%E2%80%94%20align%20with%20Project%202025%20policy%20goals%20to%20deconstruct%20the%20administrative%20state%20and%20strengthen%20the%20%26quot%3Bpresidential%20will.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBen-Ghiat%20noted%20in%20a%20recent%20Substack%20that%20%26quot%3Bit's%20as%20though%20these%20jurists%20made%20their%20decisions%20with%20Project%202025%20in%20one%20hand%20and%20an%20autocrat's%20playbook%20in%20the%20other.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20that's%20how%20it%20sort%20of%20runs%20on%20autopilot%20and%20just%20moves%2C%26quot%3B%20Carusone%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20members%20of%20Congress%20have%20already%20embraced%20policies%20that%20makeup%20portions%20of%20Project%202025's%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERep.%20Thomas%20Massie%20of%20Kentucky%20has%20repeatedly%20introduced%20measures%20to%20abolish%20the%20Education%20Department.%20Rep.%20Marjorie%20Taylor%20Greene%20of%20Georgia%20in%202022%20introduced%20a%20measure%20to%20make%20it%20a%20felony%20for%20physicians%20to%20provide%20gender-affirming%20care%20to%20children%20and%20prevent%20federal%20healthcare%20facilities%20from%20providing%20such%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOhio%20Sen.%20JD%20Vance%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0now%20Trump's%20pick%20for%20the%20vice%20presidential%20ticket%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0told%20Newsweek%20the%20project%20has%20%26quot%3Bsome%20good%20ideas.%26quot%3B%20He%20has%20previously%20supported%20abortion%20bans%20without%20exception%20for%20rape%20and%20incest%2C%20and%20in%20June%20voted%20against%20a%20bill%20that%20would%20have%20cemented%20access%20to%20in%20vitro%20fertilization%20(IVF).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20even%20partial%20control%20of%20the%20legislative%20and%20judicial%20branches%2C%20Carusone%20noted%2C%20even%20if%20Trump%20doesn't%20win%20in%20November%2C%20the%20goals%20behind%20Project%202025%20can%20still%20be%20pushed%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20you%20don't%20need%20Trump's%20thumb%20on%20the%20scale%2C%20or%20even%20his%20direction%2C%20because%20it's%20going%20to%20move%20on%20its%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20Carusone%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e3b0e459-fbed-4704-a008-c47a5a181cab%5C%22%3ETrump's%20close%20ties%20to%20Project%202025%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20president's%20proposed%20policies%20for%20his%20hypothetical%20second%20term%2C%20Agenda%2047%2C%20include%20numerous%20areas%20of%20overlap%20with%20Project%202025.%20Among%20them%20are%20the%20defunding%20of%20the%20Education%20Department%2C%20instructing%20federal%20agencies%20to%20end%20programs%20that%20promote%20sex%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fim-transgender-have-been-in-military-for-over-a-decade-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egender%20transition%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20any%20age%2C%20and%20the%20niche%20promise%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20reissue%20Executive%20Order%2013957%2C%20which%20made%20federal%20employees%20easier%20to%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20independent%20outlet%20Popular%20Information%20first%20reported%20that%2031%20of%20the%2038%20people%20who%20wrote%20and%20edited%20Project%202025%20had%20been%20either%20appointed%20or%20nominated%20to%20positions%20in%20Trump's%20first%20administration%20or%20his%20transition%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20CNN%20review%20found%20over%20140%20Trump%20administration%20members%20had%20contributed%20to%20Project%202025.%20The%20Washington%20Post%20described%20The%20Heritage%20Foundation%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Brevolving%20door%20for%20Trump%20officials.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20The%20Heritage%20Foundation%20created%20its%20%26quot%3BMandate%20for%20Leadership%26quot%3B%20ahead%20of%20Trump's%20first%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eterm%2C%20the%20conservative%20group%20proudly%20announced%20that%20Trump%20applied%2064%25%20of%20its%20policy%20recommendations%20in%20the%20first%20two%20years%20of%20his%20presidency%2C%20CBS%20News%20reported.%20The%20recommendations%20included%20leaving%20the%20Paris%20Climate%20Accords%2C%20ramping%20up%20military%20spending%2C%20and%20increasing%20offshore%20drilling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Politico%20reported%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa-nonprofit-is-training-critical-race-theory-activists-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERussell%20Vought%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Project%202025%20consultant%20and%20president%20of%20the%20conservative%20think%20tank%20The%20Center%20for%20Renewing%20America%2C%20included%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchristian-nationalism-distorts-american-and-christian-values-group-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChristian%20nationalism%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20as%20among%20the%20top%20priorities%20for%20a%20second%20Trump%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVought%2C%20the%20outlet%20reported%2C%20was%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Office%20of%20Management%20and%20Budget%20during%20Trump's%20first%20term%20and%20is%20a%20likely%20pick%20for%20his%20Chief%20of%20Staff%20if%20he's%20elected%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d1058078-5f68-47e9-a258-3c2ea54de14d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Trump%20said%20about%20Project%202025%20%E2%80%94%20and%20its%20leaders%20about%20him%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20no%20idea%20who%20is%20behind%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20wrote%20July%205%20on%20Truth%20Social.%20%26quot%3BI%20disagree%20with%20some%20of%20the%20things%20they're%20saying%20and%20some%20of%20the%20things%20they're%20saying%20are%20absolutely%20ridiculous%20and%20abysmal.%20Anything%20they%20do%2C%20I%20wish%20them%20luck%2C%20but%20I%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDanielle%20Alvarez%2C%20a%20Trump%20spokesperson%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Agenda%2047%20and%20President%20Trump's%20RNC%20Platform%20are%20the%20only%20policies%20endorsed%20by%20President%20Trump%20for%20a%20second%20term%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BTeam%20Biden%20and%20the%20DNC%20are%20LYING%20and%20fear-mongering%20because%20they%20have%20NOTHING%20else%20to%20offer%20the%20American%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20he%20denies%20knowing%20anything%20about%20the%20project%2C%20the%20playbook%20mentions%20Trump's%20name%20more%20than%20300%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKevin%20Roberts%2C%20the%20president%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freagan-heritage-foundation-economic-freedom-new-right-desantis-trump-markets-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Heritage%20Foundation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20noted%20in%20a%20July%2010%20episode%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Vince%20Coglianese%20Show%26quot%3B%20that%20there's%20a%20%26quot%3Btremendous%26quot%3B%20amount%20of%20overlap%20between%20Trump's%20Agenda%2047%20and%20Project%202025%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20standard%20Republican%20platform%20more%20generally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoberts%20said%20there%20were%20%26quot%3Bno%20hard%20feelings%20from%20any%20of%20us%20at%20Project%202025%26quot%3B%20about%20Trump's%20statement%20denouncing%20their%20agenda%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3Bhe's%20making%20a%20political%20tactical%20decision%20there%26quot%3B%20in%20response%20to%20a%20swath%20of%20bad%20press%20about%20the%20playbook's%20extreme%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20what%20you're%20going%20to%20see%20is%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20golden%20era%20of%20conservative%20reform%2C%26quot%3B%20Roberts%20added.%20%26quot%