sider.com%2Fsupreme-court-signs-code-of-conduct-lacking-an-enforcement-mechanism-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eethics%20code%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20high%20court%2C%20the%20outlet%20reported%2C%20citing%20people%20briefed%20on%20the%20plan.%20Specific%20details%20of%20the%20proposal%20%E2%80%94%20or%20when%20it%20might%20be%20officially%20announced%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0were%20not%20immediately%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20an%20existing%20code%20of%20conduct%2C%20rolled%20out%20last%20November%2C%20which%20outlines%20when%20a%20sitting%20Justice%20should%20recuse%20themselves%20from%20a%20case%20and%20when%20outside%20activities%20may%20create%20the%20appearance%20of%20a%20conflict%20of%20interest.%20However%2C%20unlike%20the%20code%20that%20binds%20lower%20court%20justices%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupreme-court-ethics-rules-missing-word-should-shall-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court's%20ethics%20code%3C%2Fa%3E%20lacks%20any%20enforcement%20mechanism.%20It%20requires%20sitting%20Justices%20to%20regulate%20themselves%2C%20with%20critics%20regarding%20the%20measures%20as%20toothless%20against%20the%20court's%20lifetime%20appointees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20changes%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20would%20require%20congressional%20approval%20to%20enact%2C%20so%20Biden%20is%20turning%20to%20his%20allies%20in%20the%20House%20and%20Senate%20for%20help%2C%20the%20Post%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20need%20your%20help%20on%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20because%20I'm%20about%20to%20come%20out%20%E2%80%94%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20prematurely%20announce%20it%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I'm%20about%20to%20come%20out%20with%20a%20major%20initiative%20on%20limiting%20the%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Post%20reported%20Biden%20said%2C%20according%20to%20a%20transcript%20of%20a%20Saturday%20call%20with%20the%20Congressional%20Progressive%20Caucus.%20%26quo