y%20nuances%20in%20personal%20finance%20that%20it's%20likely%20some%20advice%20is%20outdated%2C%20too%20generic%2C%20or%20not%20really%20suited%20to%20help%20you%20where%20you're%20at.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20that's%20why%20it's%20called%20%3Cem%3Epersonal%3C%2Fem%3E%20finance.%20Money%20moves%20are%20personal%2C%20and%20the%20best%20financial%20moves%20for%20one%20person%20won't%20work%20for%20everyone.%20The%20key%20to%20getting%20ahead%20is%20understanding%20how%20to%20work%20the%20system%20and%20doing%20your%20research%20so%20you%20can%20make%20an%20informed%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20in%20November%202021.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freasons-dont-have-emergency-fund-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721168563000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6696f1ca9caa6ed01e022f9e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freasons-dont-have-emergency-fund-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Writer%20Holly%20Johnson%20has%20ample%20assets%20in%20investments%20and%20easy%20access%20to%20credit%2C%20so%20she'd%20rather%20keep%20her%20money%20growing%20in%20the%20market.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22holly%40clubthrifty.com%20(Holly%20Johnson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freasons-dont-have-emergency-fund-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20still%20isn't%20tweeting%20%E2%80%94%20no%20matter%20how%20much%20Elon%20Musk%20gives%20him%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221368%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Donald%20Trump%20and%20Elon%20Musk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6696f03e8893442a51572c75%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C