2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20US%20Air%20Force%20is%20redesigning%20its%20next-gen%20stealth%20fighter%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20reduce%20its%20roughly%20%24300%20million%20price%20tag%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20US%20Air%20Force%20F-22%20Raptor%20flies%20above%20two%20Polish%20F-16%20jets%20against%20a%20lush%20and%20green%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668d7824268f62ba18a88459%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETwo%20Polish%20F-16s%20fly%20near%20a%20US%20Air%20Force%20F-22%20Raptor%2C%20which%20was%20expected%20to%20be%20replaced%20by%20the%20service's%20next-generation%20fighter.%3Cp%3EAir%20Force%20Staff%20Sgt.%20Danielle%20Sukhlall%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Air%20Force%20is%20redesigning%20its%20new%20stealth%20fighter%20as%20it%20struggles%20to%20fund%20its%20high-cost%20programs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20sixth-gen%20fighter's%20redesign%20aims%20to%20better%20integrate%20it%20with%20AI-piloted%20aircraft%20and%20cut%20costs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20new%20fighter%20jet%20may%20feature%20a%20less%20complex%20engine%20to%20lower%20its%20roughly%20%24300%20million%20price%20tag.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAmerica's%20new%20stealth%20fighter%2C%20being%20developed%20under%20the%20name%20Next%20Generation%20Air%20Dominance%20(or%20NGAD)%2C%20is%20not%20being%20canceled%20but%20will%20be%20redesigned%20to%20bring%20costs%20down%20and%20better%20integrate%20the%20new%20aircraft%20with%20its%20AI-enabled%20drone%20wingmen%20that%20are%20also%20in%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20decade%20of%20development%2C%20the%20future%20of%20what%20many%20have%20called%20the%20world's%20first%206th-generation%20fighter%20was%20suddenly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sandboxx.us%2Fnews%2Fthe-future-of-americas-ngad-stealth-fighter-may-be-in-question%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecalled%20into%20question%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20recent%20weeks%20as%20the%20Air%20Force%20struggles%20to%20fund%20a%20laundry%20list%20of%20high-dollar%20modernization%20programs%2C%20including%20a%20new%20stealth%20bomber%20in%20the%20B-21%20Raider%2C%20and%20a%20new%20nuclear%20intercontinental%20ballistic%20missile%20in%20the%20LGM-35A%20Sentinel%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Air%20Force%20Secretary%20Frank%20Kendall%20has%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defensenews.com%2Fair%2F2024%2F07%2F01%2Fnext-gen-fighter-not-dead-but-needs-cheaper-redesign-kendall-says%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDefense%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20effort%20to%20field%20a%20new%20stealth%20fighter%20is%20not%20dead%20but%20will%20see%20changes%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20possibility%20of%20using%20a%20less%20complex%20engine%20than%20the%20new%20adaptive%20cycle%20powerplants%20that%20have%20been%20in%20development%20for%20this%20new%20fighter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20family%20of%20systems%20concept%20of%20Next%20Generation%20Air%20Dominance%20is%20alive%20and%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Kendall%20told%20Defense%20News.%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20tell%20you%20that%20we%20are%20looking%20at%20the%20NGAD%20platform%20design%20concept%20to%20see%20if%20it's%20the%20right%20concept%20or%20not.%20We're%20looking%20at%20whether%20we%20can%20do%20something%20that's%20less%20expensive%20and%20do%20some%20trade-offs%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20Air%20Force%20Sec.%20Frank%20Kendall%2C%20Space%20Command%20Cmdr.%20James%20Dickinson%2C%20and%20Space%20Command%20Chief%20of%20Space%20Operations%20Gen.%20Chance%20Saltzman%20testify%20during%20a%20congressional%20hearing.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6696b6c78893442a51571491%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20Air%20Force%20Sec.%20Frank%20Kendall%20covers%20his%20mouth%20with%20his%20hand%20while%20testifying%20during%20a%20congressional%20hearing.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Wong%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20news%20is%20sure%20to%20cause%20some%20concern%20within%20America's%20airpower%20apparatus.%20This%20new%20fighter%2C%20after%20all%2C%20is%20arguably%20only%20in%20development%20today%20because%20of%20the%20seemingly%20short-sighted%20decision%20to%20cancel%20production%20of%20the%20F-22%20Raptor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20cost-saving%20measure%20amid%20the%20Global%20War%20on%20Terror%2C%20America's%20current%20top-tier%20air%20superiority%20fighter%20saw%20its%20production%20run%20slashed%20from%20750%20fighters%20to%20just%20186.%20This%20doomed%20the%20Raptor%20to%20a%20short%20service%20life%2C%20with%20ever-increasing%20operating%20costs%20and%20no%20way%20to%20replace%20airframes%20as%20they%20age%20out%20of%20service%20or%20are%20lost%20in%20combat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20the%20oldest%20stealth%20fighter%20in%20service%20today%2C%20the%20F-22%20Raptor%20is%20still%20arguably%20the%20healthiest%20and%20most%20dominant%20in%20air-to-air%20combat%2C%20thanks%20in%20no%20small%20part%20to%20its%20advanced%20Pratt%20%26amp%3B%20Whitney%20F119%20afterburning%20turbofan%20engines%20that%20are%20so%20powerful%20they%20can%20produce%20more%20thrust%20without%20their%20afterburners%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethan%20the%20F-15%20Eagle%20can%20with%20its%20afterburners%20at%20full%20tilt.%20They%20also%20offer%20significant%20thermal%20and%20radar%20signature%20reduction%20for%20improved%20stealth%20and%20thrust%20vector%20control%20(or%20the%20ability%20to%20orient%20the%20outflow%20of%20thrust%20independent%20of%20the%20airframe)%20for%20improved%20aerobatic%20maneuverability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20advanced%20engine%20also%20serves%20as%20the%20basis%20for%20the%20F-35's%20F135%20turbofan%2C%20which%20is%20the%20most%20powerful%20turbofan%20engine%20ever%20affixed%20to%20a%20fighter%20to%20date.%20Yet%2C%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20both%20China%20and%20Russia%20have%20begun%20production%20on%20their%20own%20seemingly%20comparable%20fifth-generation%20engines%2C%20eroding%20the%20technological%20advantage%20the%20already%20endangered%20F-22%20enjoys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22F-22%20performs%20aerial%20maneuvers%20during%20an%20open%20house%20event%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6671c6392efa138e0330b7f4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20Air%20Force%20Maj.%20Paul%20Lopez%20performs%20aerial%20maneuvers%20during%20an%20open%20house%20event%20on%20Malmstrom%20Air%20Force%20Base.%3Cp%3EUS%20Air%20Force%20photo%20by%20Airman%201st%20Class%20Jacob%20M.%20Thompson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGE%20and%20Pratt%20%26amp%3B%20Whitney%20have%20been%20hard%20at%20work%20for%20years%20developing%20new%20engines%20for%20America's%20new%20fighter%20as%20a%20part%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sandboxx.us%2Fnews%2Fthe-race-to-field-the-most-advanced-stealth-fighter-engines-in-the-world%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENext-Generation%20Adaptive%20Propulsion%20(NGAP)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20both%20of%20the%20competing%20designs%20promising%20to%20offer%20a%20significant%20leap%20in%20both%20fuel%20economy%20and%20power%20production.%20And%20although%20testing%20has%20been%20promising%20with%20these%20engines%20(particularly%20for%20GE's%20XA100)%2C%20it%20seems%20this%20may%20be%20one%20of%20the%20areas%20the%20Air%20Force%20believes%20it%20can%20reduce%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20last%20numbers%20I%20saw%20on%20NGAP%20%5BNext%20Generation%20Adaptive%20Propulsion%5D%20were%20pretty%20high%2C%26quot%3B%20retired%20General%20Clint%20Hinote%2C%20who%20was%20previously%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20Air%