A%20Congress'%20Digvijaya%20Singh%20Tells%20Youth%20Party%20Workers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20veteran%20Digvijaya%20Singh%20on%20Tuesday%20asked%20agitating%20Youth%20Congress%20workers%20to%20learn%20from%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20on%20how%20to%20convey%20the%20message%20effectively%20and%20focus%20on%20expanding%20the%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20was%20addressing%20a%20sit-in%20protest%20organised%20by%20the%20Youth%20Congress%20against%20the%20alleged%20nursing%20college%20scam%20and%20NEET%20paper%20leak%20in%20Jabalpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLearn%20from%20RSS%20though%20we%20are%20their%20staunch%20opponents.%20They%20play%20mind%20games.%20They%20will%20never%20protest%2C%20never%20stage%20demonstrations%2C%20never%20get%20beaten%20up%2C%20and%20will%20never%20go%20to%20jail%2C%20but%20rather%20they%20will%20send%20us%20to%20jail%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20said%20holding%20protests%20will%20not%20prove%20effective%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20grassroots%20organisational%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20suggested%20holding%20agitations%20at%20three%20levels%20ranging%20from%20booth%20to%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRSS%20normally%20focuses%20on%20three%20things%3A%20distributing%20pamphlets%2C%20holding%20discussions%2C%20and%20finally%20the%20expenses%20incurred%20on%20the%20movement.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20fight%20them%2C%20beat%20them%20in%20their%20own%20game%2C%20of%20course%2C%20not%20physically%20but%20intellectually%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20said%20RSS%20could%20be%20countered%20effectively%20by%20understanding%20their%20modus%20operandi%20and%20propaganda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20talking%20to%20reporters%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20expressed%20disappointment%20over%20the%20Congress%20party's%20performance%20in%20the%20state%20elections%2C%20sta