referrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fhow-to-turn-pomegranate-mango-orange-peels-into-fertilisers-for-your-garden%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efruit%20peels%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Soak%20the%20peels%20in%20water%20for%20a%20week%2C%20then%20strain%20out%20the%20water%20and%20add%20it%20to%20the%20plants.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUse%20cow%20dung%20fertiliser%20during%20the%20flowering%20stage.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20tomatoes%20will%20be%20ready%20to%20harvest%20in%20about%20three%20months.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Pumpkin%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPumpkins%20can%20be%20planted%20during%20July-August.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESow%20seeds%20in%20a%20seedling%20tray%3B%20the%20seeds%20will%20germinate%20within%20seven%20days.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETransfer%20them%20to%20a%20large%20container%20as%20they%20grow.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPlant%20only%20one%20sapling%20in%20a%20container.%20You%20can%20grow%20this%20vine%20crop%20in%20a%2024-inch%20pot.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFlowering%20will%20start%20in%2030%20days%2C%20and%20pumpkins%20will%20be%20ready%20to%20harvest%20in%20about%2090%20days%20from%20planting.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjuly-vegetables-5-1656927723-1721135593.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20ridge%20gourd%20plant%20will%20start%20yielding%20in%20about%20four%20months.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjuly-vegetables-5-1656927723-1721135593.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjuly-vegetables-5-1656927723-1721135593-300x170.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F