Cp%3EWhile%20it%20sounds%20great%20on%20paper%2C%20once%20the%20soil%20gets%20used%20to%20chemical%20fertilisers%2C%20it%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20and%20patience%20to%20revive%20it%20or%20bring%20it%20back%20to%20its%20former%20glory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFundamentally%2C%20soil%20or%20plants%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20anything%20non-natural.%20Chemicals%20are%20alien%2C%20but%20once%20you%E2%80%99ve%20pumped%20them%20in%20for%20decades%2C%20they%20get%20used%20to%20it.%20So%20we%20started%20with%20a%20small%20portion%20of%20land.%20The%20first%20and%20most%20important%20thing%20to%20do%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F351690%2Fyash-dayal-sharma-fertile-beeghas-organic-waste-vermicompost-stubble-burning-train-farmers-soil-health%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efocus%20on%20the%20soil%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20using%20cow%20dung%20and%20vermicompost.%20While%20in%20chemical%20farming%20one%20tends%20to%20kill%20pests%2C%20one%20of%20the%20principles%20of%20natural%20farming%20is%20that%20pests%20are%20integral%20and%20can%20co-exist.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20soil%20started%20regaining%20its%20health%2C%20he%20started%20multi-cropping.%20Pulses%20and%20flowers%20would%20be%20grown%20together.%20After%20a%20few%20months%2C%20he%20saw%20good%20results.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20output%20might%20not%20have%20been%20equal%20to%20the%20one%20earlier%2C%20it%20was%20free%20of%20harmful%20chemicals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeeping%20at%20this%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20brought%20their%20harvest%20back%20to%20original%20numbers.%20Buoyed%20by%20the%20results%2C%20he%20expanded%20to%20growing%20other%20pulses%20at%20the%20farm%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%