20every%20morning%2C%20her%20enthusiasm%20is%20evident.%20After%20all%2C%20she%20is%20living%20her%20dream.%20But%20her%20story%20is%20not%20in%20isolation%3B%20it%20echoes%20the%20untapped%20potential%20that%20lies%20within%20many%20%E2%80%9CEntrepreneurial%20Households%E2%80%9D%20such%20as%20hers%20across%20India%2C%20even%20in%20small%20towns%2C%20cities%20and%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EPIC%20Stories%20Video%20contest%20organised%20by%20Enmasse%20World%20in%20collaboration%20with%20The%20Better%20India%20was%20an%20attempt%20at%20underscoring%20the%20journeys%20of%20millions%20like%20Geetha%20who%20are%20the%20drivers%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20next%20economic%20wave.%20The%20contest%20called%20for%20entries%20from%20across%20the%20country%20of%20people%20who%20are%20turning%20their%20dreams%20and%20aspirations%20into%20reality%20by%20doing%20a%20range%20of%20things%2C%20from%20starting%20businesses%20to%20innovating%20in%20everyday%20life%2C%20thus%20bringing%20financial%20growth%20to%20their%20households.%20Storytellers%20from%20all%20corners%20of%20India%20joined%20in%20and%20the%20contest%20provided%20them%20with%20the%20stage%20to%20bring%20the%20struggles%20and%20victories%20of%20Entrepreneurial%20Households%20(a%20term%20coined%20by%20Enmasse)%20to%20light.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20are%20Entrepreneurial%20Households%3F%20You%E2%80%99ll%20recognise%20them%20as%20savvy%2C%20business-minded%2C%20resilient%20households%20with%20multiple%20income%20streams%20and%20strategic%20borrowings%2C%20all%20leveraged%20for%20growth%2C%20and%20you%E2%80%99ll%20find%20them%20all%20around%20you%2C%20and%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%20of%20the%20contest%2C%20thus%2C%20was%20to%20send%20out%20a%20clear%20message%20that%20these%20homes%20are%20no%20longer%20a%20sidenote%20in%20the%20margins.%20They%20hold%20the%20transformative%20power%20to%20shape%20the%20future%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20economy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20contest%20like%20this%20provides%20the%20opportunity%20for%20existing%20and%20new%20entrepreneurs%20and%20business%20leaders%20to%20move%20the%20gaze%20away%20from%20big%20cities%20and%20disposable%20incomes%20to%20small%20towns%20and%20core%20services%2C%20and%20they%E2%80%99ll%20find%20that%20the%20market%20potential%20is%20immense.%20Enmasse%20World%20calls%20this%20the%20Economic%20Power%20of%20Industrious%20Communities%2C%20or%20the%20EPIC%20Opportunity.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20new%20age%20creed%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%202022%20story%2C%20%3Cem%3EForbes%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20called%20owners%20of%20small%20home%20businesses%20the%20%E2%80%98OG%20entrepreneurs%E2%80%99.%20The%20moniker%20is%20backed%20by%20statistics.%20According%20to%20a%202024%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EPraxis%20Global%20Alliance%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20Enmasse%20World%2C%20in%20FY%202023%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20247%20million%20entrepreneurial%20households%20drove%20an%20%248.8%20trillion%20transaction%20value%20%E2%80%94%20with%20a%20significant%20portion%20being%20informal%20transactions%2C%20unleashing%20a%20new%20economic%20landscape.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20in%20home-owned%20businesses%20and%20their%20success%20are%20a%20nod%20to%20the%20notion%20that%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20economic%20prospects%20do%20not%20necessarily%20lie%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20commercial%20enterprises.%20But%20rather%2C%20that%20magic%20can%20often%20be%20brewed%20in%20the%20smallest%20of%20farms%20and%20home%20kitchens.%20That%E2%80%99s%20where%20India%E2%80%99s%20collective%20growth%20story%20is%20unfolding%2C%20every%20single%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20sr