when%20the%20couple%20moved%20to%20their%20bungalow%20in%20Goodwill%20community%2C%20the%20obvious%20choice%20was%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352016%2Fhow-to-harvest-solar-energy-panels-in-apartments-homes-rentals-guide-to-save-electricity-bills%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einstall%20solar%20panels%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20house%20was%20constructed%20in%201984.%20After%20we%20became%20parents%2C%20we%20moved%20into%20one%20of%20the%20newer%20modern%20complexes%20where%20the%20kids%20could%20have%20more%20friend%20circles%2C%20better%20schools%20and%20amenities.%20Now%20that%20they%20are%20grown%20up%2C%20we%20moved%20back%20to%20the%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shilpa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%20Suneet%2C%20who%20was%20always%20interested%20in%20reducing%20their%20energy%20footprint%20and%20adopting%20sustainable%20manners%20of%20living%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20wife%20encouraged%20me%20to%20be%20enthused%20and%20come%20up%20with%20solutions%20where%20we%20did%20not%20compromise%20on%20our%20quality%20and%20standard%20of%20living.%20Otherwise%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20very%20easy%20to%20cut%20down%20on%20this%20and%20be%20sustainable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20decided%20to%20go%20off-grid.%20%E2%80%9CNormally%2C%20people%20believe%20that%20large%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fsolar-powered-homes-of-india-rooftop-panels-save-electricity-bills%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar%20PV%20installations%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecan%20only%20be%20done%20for%20farmhouses.%20We%20wanted%20to%20prove%20that%20we%20can%20lead%20sustainable%20lives%20even%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20bustling%20city%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shilpa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20moving%20to%20the%20bungalow%2C%20the%20couple%20installed%2042%20panels%20of%202%C3%9