een%20IAS%20and%20IFS%20and%20the%20preparation%20strategy%20that%20led%20him%20to%20success%20in%20his%20first%20attempt%20at%20IFS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDecade-long%20journey%20to%20becoming%20an%20IFS%20Officer%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20from%20Jalandhar%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Harsimran%20shares%20the%20story%20behind%20his%20inspiration%20to%20join%20the%20civil%20services.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20a%20child%2C%20my%20mother%20would%20tell%20me%20stories%20about%20her%20dream%20of%20becoming%20an%20IAS%20officer.%20However%2C%20at%20that%20time%2C%20the%20environment%20was%20not%20conducive%20for%20women%20to%20pursue%20higher%20education%20and%20jobs.%20Opportunities%20were%20limited%2C%20and%20parents%20primarily%20focused%20on%20marrying%20off%20their%20daughters.%20She%20hoped%20to%20fulfil%20her%20dream%20through%20me%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20achieve%20this%20for%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20civil%20engineering%20degree%20from%20the%20DAV%20Institute%20of%20Engineering%20and%20Technology%20in%202013%2C%20Harsimran%20worked%20in%20the%20private%20sector%20for%20a%20year.%20In%202014%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20leave%20his%20job%20and%20prepare%20full-time%20for%20the%20UPSC-CSE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarsimran%20cleared%20the%20Prelims%20on%20his%20first%20attempt%20but%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20clear%20the%20Mains.%20This%20pattern%20continued%20in%20his%20successive%20attempts%20in%202015%20and%202016.%20In%202017%2C%20he%20managed%20to%20clear%20the%20Mains%20but%20did%20not%20make%20it%20to%20the%20final%20list%20after%20the%20interview%20round.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20that%20time%2C%20I%20was%20unemployed%2C%20and%20I%20was%20not%20getting%20success%20in%20my%20attempts.%20I%20was%20disheartened%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20felt%20it%20was%20high%20time%20to%20work%20on%20his%20Plan%20B%20%E2%80%94%20securing%20a%20government%20position%20in%20the%20Punj