%20This%20exam%20isn%E2%80%99t%20everything.%20It%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20diversify%20and%20not%20put%20all%20your%20eggs%20in%20one%20basket.%20That%20should%20be%20your%20initial%20approach.%20Many%20people%20waste%20years%20chasing%20glamour.%20Instead%2C%20dedicate%20two%20to%20three%20years%20of%20hard%20work%2C%20and%20if%20you%E2%80%99re%20unable%20to%20clear%20it%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20perfectly%20fine%20to%20explore%20other%20opportunities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F308203%2Fhow-to-prepare-for-upsc-cse-for-working-professionals-ias-divya-mittal-shares-tips-on-twitter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlongside%20your%20job%2C%20you%20can%20prepare%20for%20this%20exam%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Hard%20work%20never%20goes%20to%20waste%3B%20I%20can%20attest%20to%20this%20after%20almost%2010%20years%20of%20my%20journey%2C%20which%20fortunately%20culminated%20in%20success%20in%20this%20field%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20he%20began%20preparing%20for%20forest%20services%20alongside%20his%20full-time%20job.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20this%20was%20my%20last%20opportunity%20to%20get%20into%20the%20service%2C%20I%20was%20nervous.%20But%20finally%2C%20I%20tasted%20success%20in%20my%20first%20attempt%20at%20IFS%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Harsimran%2C%20who%20clenched%20an%20AIR%20of%2016%20in%20the%202022%20examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIAS%20vs%20IFS%20%E2%80%94%20How%20different%20is%20the%20preparation%20process%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20UPSC%2C%20candidates%20can%20choose%20their%20preferred%20ranks%2C%20opting%20for%20either%20IAS%2C%20IFS%2C%20or%20both.%20They%20have%20separate%20attempts%20for%20each.%20Initially%2C%20Harsimran%20focused%20solely%20on%20IAS%20(CSE).%20However%2C%20on%20his%20final%20attempt%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20pursue%20IFS%2C%20a%20decision%20that%20proved%20fruitful%20as%20he%20