%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-09-at-11.48.13-AM-1720526791.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20first%20Meditel%20model%20that%20Nikhil%20built%20when%20he%20was%20in%20Class%207%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-09-at-11.48.13-AM-1720526791.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-09-at-11.48.13-AM-1720526791-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-09-at-11.48.13-AM-1720526791-500x281.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-09-at-11.48.13-AM-1720526791-768x432.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-09-at-11.48.13-AM-1720526791-150x84.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356097%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20first%20Meditel%20model%20that%20Nikhil%20built%20when%20he%20was%20in%20Class%207%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Nikhil%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20just%20wanted%20to%20help%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20known%20fact%20that%20skipping%20one%E2%80%99s%20medicine%20dosage%20is%20to%20the%20detriment%20of%20good%20health.%20But%20as%20Nikhil%20soon%20deduced%2C%20medication%20non-adherence%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20one-pronged%20problem.%20It%20had%20many%20facets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20first%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20come%20up%20with%20an%20alarm%20system%20that%20would%20alert%20people%20when%20they%20needed%20to%20take%20their%20pills.%20But%2C%20eventually%2C%20as%20I%20observed%20my%20grandmother%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20even%20when%20she%20did%20remember%2C%20but%20did%20not%20have%20water%20handy%2C%20she%20would%20put%20it%20off%20for%20later.%E2%80%9D%20This%20led%20to%20Nikhil%20integrating%20a%20reusable%20water%20bottle%20into%20the%20device%2C%20attached%20by%20velcro.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20component%20was%20the%20pill%20organiser%2C%20born%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20help%20people%20who%20were%20prescribed%20multiple%20doses%20specific%20to%20their%20meal%20times.%20%E2%80%9CMeditel%20allows%20users%20to%20set%20up%20to%20six%20daily%20alarms%2C%20accommodating%20various%20medication%20schedules%20like%20pre%2Fpost%20breakfast%2C%20lunch%2C%20and%20dinner%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nikhil%20explains.%20Sourcing%20the%20parts%20and%20putting%20the%20device%20together%20was%20one%20thing%20but%20coding%20to%20get%20the%20alarm%20systems%20in%20place%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20challenge.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20essentially%20the%20first%20model%20I%20was%20ever%20building%20from%20scratch%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nikhil%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20became%20savvy%20with%20the%20arduino%20%E2%80%94%20an%20open-source%20coding%20board%20%E2%80%94%20that%20sends%20a%20signal%20to%20the%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20device%20to%20control%20their%20working.%E2%80%9D%20The%20journey%20was%20fraught%20with%20learning%20and%20spanned%20months%2C%20with%20Nikhil%20refining%20his%20coding%20skills%2C%20sharpening%20his%20technical%20palette%20and%20perfecting%20Meditel%20with%20each%20learning.%20He%20credits%20his%20parents%20for%20their%20support%20through%20these%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FF_YjhVca0AANDEO-1720527218.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nikhil%20was%20a%20panellist%20at%20the%20World%20Children's%20Day%20conference%20at%20New%20Delhi%20in%202023%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FF_YjhV